    • 方法详细资料

      • initialize

        public void initialize()
        initialize the score page to load data into ListView.

      • ReadFile

        public void ReadFile()
        Read scores from file and add them into ListView. Read files from relative location and read line by line to get the score for each time. Store all the double value into ListView.

      • SortList

        public void SortList()
        Sort the ListView from high score to lower one. Get each double value of score and then use bubble sort to make them in decent order.

      • AddOrder

        public void AddOrder()
        Add order to each score.

      • showHighest

        public void showHighest()
        If this score is the highest score, show the image of the highest.
